<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>DataVC</title>
  <!-- CSS only -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="container">
    <header class="d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center py-3 mb-4 border-bottom">
      <a href="/" class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3 mb-md-0 me-md-auto text-dark text-decoration-none">
        <svg class="bi me-2" width="40" height="32">
          <use xlink:href="#bootstrap" />
        </svg>
        <span class="fs-4">VDC</span>
      </a>

      <ul class="nav nav-pills">
        <li class="nav-item"><a href="Homepage.html" class="nav-link active" aria-current="page">Home</a></li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a href="#hanging-icons" class="nav-link">Features</a></li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a href="#accordionFlushExample" class="nav-link">FAQs</a></li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a href="#" class="nav-link">About</a></li>
      </ul>
    </header>
  </div>




  <!-- sign in -->

  <div class="container col-xl-10 col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5">
    <div class="row align-items-center g-lg-5 py-5">
      <div class="col-lg-7 text-center text-lg-start">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3">Visualization of data correlation</h1>
        <p class="col-lg-10 fs-4">A web application tool that helps users to simplify data by vizualizing it in beauteful charts.<br> By choosing population, users will be able to identify correlations between individual attributes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-10 mx-auto col-lg-5">

        <form action="/login" method="POST" class="p-4 p-md-5 border rounded-3 bg-light">
          <% if(msg){ %>
          <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
            <%= msg %>
          </div>
          <%  } %>


          <div class="form-floating mb-3">
            <input type="email" name="username" class="form-control" id="floatingInput" placeholder="name@example.com">
            <label for="floatingInput">Email address</label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-floating mb-3">
            <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" id="floatingPassword" placeholder="Password" required>
            <label for="floatingPassword">Password</label>
          </div>
          <button class="w-100 btn btn-lg btn-primary" type="submit">Sign in</button>
          <p style="text-align:center ">Forgot password? <a class="hide_UnderLine" href="#">here</a></p>
          <p style="text-align:center ">Don't have an account? <a class="hide_UnderLine" href="/register">Sign Up</a></p>

          <hr class="my-4">

          <small class="text-muted">By clicking Sign up, you will move to the sign up page.</small> <!-- remove?? -->
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Features -->


  <div class="container px-4 py-5" id="hanging-icons">
    <h2 class="pb-2 border-bottom">Features</h2>
    <div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">
      <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
        <div class="icon-square text-bg-light d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-4 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
          <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em">
            <use xlink:href="#cpu-fill" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>manage your datasets</h2>
          <p>You will be able to save as many datasets as you want, and use them whenever you like!<br>
            A sidebar will contain every dataset you uploaded, from there you can upload, delete or use your datasets.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
        <div class="icon-square text-bg-light d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-4 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
          <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em">
            <use xlink:href="#tools" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Great visualization of data</h2>
          <p> To have the best user experince,<br>
            Our tool has five different charts to choose from.<br>
            Not only that, but you will be able to filter and add data in the chart in a very user friendly way!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
        <div class="icon-square text-bg-light d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center fs-4 flex-shrink-0 me-3">
          <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em">
            <use xlink:href="#toggles2" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Secure tool</h2>
          <p>VDC will keep you passwords hashed in the database <br>
            We also use sessions to insure that the user is secure and has the safest experince using our tool</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQs -->
  <div class="container px-4 py-5">

    <div class="accordion accordion-flush " id="accordionFlushExample">
      <h2 class="">FAQs</h2>

      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingOne">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseOne">
            What can I upload?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="flush-collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
          <div class="accordion-body">Our tool reads .csv files, please make sure that you're uploading the right format
            <!--move to anthor page explains the format-->
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingTwo">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseTwo">
            How can I upload my file?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="flush-collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
          <div class="accordion-body">- First make sure you file ends with ".csv"<br>
            - Then make sure that the first contains your column names<br>
            - Second row should be data types with this syntax: "_id" (always first),"Number", "String", "Double"<br>
            - After you meet all requirements click on the upload button on the side bar and choose your file name</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingThree">
          <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseThree">
            What can i customized in a chart?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="flush-collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
          <div class="accordion-body">You will be able to choose a population by filling the population form<br>
            Then you can choose what columns you like to be vizualized<br>
            finally you can choose chart types, add or filter columns, change color and finally download the chart</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <div class="container">
    <footer class="py-3 my-4">
      <p class="text-center text-muted">VDC - King Saud University</p>
    </footer>
  </div>





  <!-- JavaScript Bundle with Popper -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-A3rJD856KowSb7dwlZdYEkO39Gagi7vIsF0jrRAoQmDKKtQBHUuLZ9AsSv4jD4Xa" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</body>

</html>